## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="4b460-228">时间将默认为 UTC。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4b460-228">The time will default to UTC.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4b460-229">如果你想要指定本地时间的时间，则指定<xref:System.DateTime.Kind%2A>的属性`time`对象作为<xref:System.DateTimeKind.Local?displayProperty=nameWithType>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4b460-229">If you want to specify the time in local time, then specify the <xref:System.DateTime.Kind%2A> property of the `time` object as <xref:System.DateTimeKind.Local?displayProperty=nameWithType>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="4b460-230">下面的代码连接到服务器上的端口号"5000。"的"adamHost1.fabrikam.com"承载的 ADAM 实例</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4b460-230">The following code connects to the ADAM instance hosted by the server "adamHost1.fabrikam.com" on port number "5000."</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4b460-231">中指定的用户名 (adamAdmin) 和密码 (SecretPwd123)<xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext>构造函数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4b460-231">The username (adamAdmin), and password (SecretPwd123) are specified in the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.AccountManagement.PrincipalContext> constructor.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="4b460-232">为容器下的所有可进行身份验证主体执行搜索"DC = adamApp1，DC = fabrikam，DC = com"的具有未登录到此 ADAM 实例最近 45 天内。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4b460-232">A search is performed for all authenticable principals under the container "DC=adamApp1,DC=fabrikam,DC=com" that have not logged on to this ADAM instance for the last 45 days.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4b460-233">然后删除搜索返回的主体。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4b460-233">The principals returned by the search are then deleted.</span></span>  
  
```  
PrincipalContext ctx = new PrincipalContext(  
                                      ContextType.ApplicationDirectory,   
                                      "adamHost1.fabrikam.com:5000",   
                                      "DC=adamApp1,DC=fabrikam,DC=com",   
                                      "adamAdmin", "SecretPwd123");  
  
PrincipalSearchResult<AuthenticablePrincipal> oldPrincipals =   
                     AuthenticablePrincipal.FindByLogonTime(ctx,   
                            (DateTime.Now - new TimeSpan(45, 0, 0, 0)),   
                            MatchType.LessThan);  
  
foreach (Principal p in oldPrincipals)  
{  
    p.Delete();  
}  
  
oldPrincipals.Dispose();  
ctx.Dispose();  
  
```

